quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,160,"kadhdhabt qawm lut brsalth, fakanuu bhdha mukadhibin lsayr rusul allh; li'ana ma jawu bih min altwhyd waswl alshraye wahd"
  26,161,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum lwt: 'alaa takhshawn eadhab allh? 'iiniy rasul min rbkm, 'amin ealaa tblygh risalatah 'ilykm, fahdharuu eiqab allah ealaa tkdhybkm rswlh, watbewny fima daeawtukum 'ilyh, wama 'as'alukum ealaa dewty lhdaytkm ay ajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,162,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum lwt: 'alaa takhshawn eadhab allh? 'iiniy rasul min rbkm, 'amin ealaa tblygh risalatah 'ilykm, fahdharuu eiqab allah ealaa tkdhybkm rswlh, watbewny fima daeawtukum 'ilyh, wama 'as'alukum ealaa dewty lhdaytkm ay ajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,163,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum lwt: 'alaa takhshawn eadhab allh? 'iiniy rasul min rbkm, 'amin ealaa tblygh risalatah 'ilykm, fahdharuu eiqab allah ealaa tkdhybkm rswlh, watbewny fima daeawtukum 'ilyh, wama 'as'alukum ealaa dewty lhdaytkm ay ajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,164,"'idh qal lahum 'akhuhum lwt: 'alaa takhshawn eadhab allh? 'iiniy rasul min rbkm, 'amin ealaa tblygh risalatah 'ilykm, fahdharuu eiqab allah ealaa tkdhybkm rswlh, watbewny fima daeawtukum 'ilyh, wama 'as'alukum ealaa dewty lhdaytkm ay ajr, ma 'ajri 'iilaa ealaa rabi alealmyn"
  26,165,"atnkhwn aldhukur min bani adm, wttrkwn ma khalaq allah lastmtaekm wtnaslkm min azwajkm? bal 'antum qawm - bhdhh almesyt- mtjawzwn ma abahh allah lakum min alhlal 'iilaa alhram"
  26,166,"atnkhwn aldhukur min bani adm, wttrkwn ma khalaq allah lastmtaekm wtnaslkm min azwajkm? bal 'antum qawm - bhdhh almesyt- mtjawzwn ma abahh allah lakum min alhlal 'iilaa alhram"
  26,167,"qal qawm lwt: layin lam ttrk ya lut nahyana ean 'ityan aldhukur wtqbyh felh, latakunana min almtrwdyn min bladna"
  26,168,"qal lut lhm: 'iiniy liemlkm aldhy temlwnh min 'ityan aldhkwr, lamn almbghdyn lah bghdana shdydana"
  26,169,"thm daea lut rabih hinama yayis min astjabthm lah qayla rbb anqdhny wa'anqadh 'ahli mimaa yemlh qawmi min hadhih almesyt alqbyht, wmin eqwbtk alty stsybhm"
  26,170,"fnjynah wa'ahl baytih walmstjybyn ldewth 'ajmaein 'iilaa ejwzana min ahlh, wahi amrath, lm tsharkhm fi al'iyman, fkant min albaqin fi aleadhab walhlak"
  26,171,"fnjynah wa'ahl baytih walmstjybyn ldewth 'ajmaein 'iilaa ejwzana min ahlh, wahi amrath, lm tsharkhm fi al'iyman, fkant min albaqin fi aleadhab walhlak"
  26,172,"thm 'ahlakna man edahm min alkafarat ashdd 'ihlak, wa'anzalna ealayhim hijaratan min alsama' kalmtr ahlkthm, fqabuh mtr min 'andharahum rusuluhum walam yastajibuu lhm; faqad 'unzl bihim ashdd 'anwae alhlak waltdmyr"
  26,173,"thm 'ahlakna man edahm min alkafarat ashdd 'ihlak, wa'anzalna ealayhim hijaratan min alsama' kalmtr ahlkthm, fqabuh mtr min 'andharahum rusuluhum walam yastajibuu lhm; faqad 'unzl bihim ashdd 'anwae alhlak waltdmyr"
  26,174,"'in fi dhalik aleiqab aladhi nazal biqawm lut laebrt wmwezt, ytez biha almkdhbwn. wama kan 'aktharuhum mwmnyn"
  26,175,"w'in rabak lahu aleaziz alghalb aldhy yqhr almkdhbyn, alrahim bieibadih almwmnyn"